snippet.title: Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity - Expansion Pass Wave 2 DLC
snippet.description:
The second wave of Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity Expansion Pass DLC content is now available, including a newly playable character duo, additional stages, and emotional new story sequences.

https://zelda.com/hyrule-warriors/buy/#expansion
